OL,3,CMum prepares to fly to Majorca after
OL,4,Cson goes missing while on holiday
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man has been reported as
OL,7,Fmissing while on holiday in Majorca.
OL,9,FBenjamin Ross, from Golborne, in
OL,10,FWigan, has not been heard from since
OL,11,Fspeaking to his mum on 10 July.
OL,13,FBen, who had travelled to the Spanish
OL,14,Fisland in June to visit a friend
OL,15,Fbefore deciding to extend his stay and
OL,16,Fmoving into a temporary rental after
OL,17,Ffinding a local job, last spoke to his
OL,18,Fmum Felix almost a week ago.
