OL,3,CMum prepares to fly to Majorca after
OL,4,Cson goes missing while on holiday
OL,6,FFelix said the pair had been trying to
OL,7,Farrange a bank transfer for Ben to
OL,8,Fsupport him financially after he had
OL,9,Fhis phone, passport, keys and wallet
OL,10,Fstolen while he was going for a swim
OL,11,Fat the beach.
OL,13,FHis mum Felix said after speaking with
OL,14,Fhim, he was not "in a good place" and
OL,15,Fsent her a 'peculiar' email on 10 July.
OL,17,FSince then, communication has been cut
OL,18,Foff and neither she, nor his friend,
OL,19,Fhave heard from him.
