OL,3,CMum prepares to fly to Majorca after
OL,4,Cson goes missing while on holiday
OL,6,FThe 26-year-old, who was previously
OL,7,Ftraining as a barrister in Manchester,
OL,8,Fhas since been reported as missing.
OL,10,FBen's whereabouts currently remain
OL,11,Funknown and the Foreign Office say it
OL,12,Fis supporting his family and is "in
OL,13,Fcontact with local authorities".
OL,15,FFelix also said she has also been in
OL,16,Fcontact with LBT Global, the overseas
OL,17,Fcharity supporting Jay Slater's
OL,18,Ffamily, and is planning to fly out to
OL,19,FMajorca over the coming days.
