OL,3,CMum prepares to fly to Majorca after
OL,4,Cson goes missing while on holiday
OL,6,FShe said: "Like any mother, no matter
OL,7,Fwhat age your children are, they are
OL,8,Fstill your children. I just need to
OL,9,Fknow my son is safe and well.
OL,11,F"The last few days have been torture.
OL,12,FPlease, if anyone has seen Ben, even
OL,13,Fif it's just for a second, let the
OL,14,Fauthorities know. We need to find him."
OL,16,FA Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,17,FDevelopment Office spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"We are supporting the family of a
OL,19,FBritish man reported missing in Spain
OL,20,Fand are in contact with the local
OL,21,Fauthorities."
